    <title class="- topic/title "><ph class="- topic/ph topic/title-wrapper ">Zotero标签的管理</ph></title>
    <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc "/>
    <body class="- topic/body ">
        <p class="- topic/p ">本节介绍如何在 Zotero 中使用标签功能实现文献的高效管理。</p>
        <p class="- topic/p "/>
    </body>
<concept class="- topic/topic concept/concept " id="unique_2" topicrefclass="- map/topicref " nd:nd-id="concept_q1r_c5d_ldc" oid="concept_q1r_c5d_ldc" specializations="@props/deliveryTarget">
    <title class="- topic/title "><ph class="- topic/ph topic/title-wrapper ">6.1 为什么使用标签功能？</ph></title>
    <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc "/>
    <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
        <p class="- topic/p ">解释文件夹与标签功能的区别，以及使用标签的场景。</p>
        <p class="- topic/p "/>
        <p class="- topic/p ">在 Zotero 中，我们可以使用文件夹和标签来管理文献。文件夹适用于将文献按专题或研究方向分类，但有时一篇文献可能属于多个类别，这时使用标签更为方便。例如：<ul class="- topic/ul " id="unique_2_Connect_42_ul_o1b_m5d_ldc" nd:nd-id="ul_o1b_m5d_ldc">
                <li class="- topic/li ">将文献分类为"已读"或"未读"</li>
                <li class="- topic/li ">给特定项目编号的文献打标签<p class="- topic/p ">相比将文献复制到多个文件夹或创建子文件夹，使用标签可以简化操作，实现“交叉”管理。</p></li>
            </ul></p>
    </conbody>
</concept><task class="- topic/topic task/task " id="unique_3" topicrefclass="- map/topicref " nd:nd-id="manage_tags" oid="manage_tags" specializations="@props/deliveryTarget">
    <title class="- topic/title "><ph class="- topic/ph topic/title-wrapper ">6.2 标签基本功能</ph></title>
    <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc ">如何不显示、删除和禁用自动标签，以及为文献添加标签。</shortdesc>
    <taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody ">
        <context class="- topic/section task/context ">
            <p class="- topic/p "/>
        </context>
        <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">不显示自动标签</cmd>
                <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
                    <p class="- topic/p ">当 Zotero 导入文献时，自动标签功能会将关键词和主题导入为标签，可能导致标签区域杂乱。以下是不xian sh自动标签的方法：</p>
                </info>
                <substeps class="- topic/ol task/substeps ">
                    <substep class="- topic/li task/substep ">
                        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">打开标签管理区域</cmd>
                    </substep>
                    <substep class="- topic/li task/substep ">
                        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">点击左下角的漏斗图标</cmd>
                    </substep>
                    <substep class="- topic/li task/substep ">
                        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">取消勾选"显示自动标签"<image class="- topic/image " href="file:/Users/mac/Desktop/2024入学/课程/技术写作/中期报告/6.%20标签管理/6-image/1使自动标签不显示或删除自动标签.png" id="unique_3_Connect_42_image_uzz_nvd_ldc" nd:nd-id="image_uzz_nvd_ldc" placement="inline" width="300"/></cmd>
                    </substep>
                </substeps>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">删除现有自动标签</cmd>
                <substeps class="- topic/ol task/substeps " id="unique_3_Connect_42_substeps_mrx_nwd_ldc" nd:nd-id="substeps_mrx_nwd_ldc">
                    <substep class="- topic/li task/substep ">
                        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">点击"删除此文献库中的自动标签..."，并确认删除操作。 <image class="- topic/image " href="file:/Users/mac/Desktop/2024入学/课程/技术写作/中期报告/6.%20标签管理/6-image/2确认删除自动标签.png" id="unique_3_Connect_42_image_ok4_rwd_ldc" nd:nd-id="image_ok4_rwd_ldc" placement="inline" width="300"/></cmd>
                    </substep>
                </substeps>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">禁用自动标签</cmd>
                <substeps class="- topic/ol task/substeps " id="unique_3_Connect_42_substeps_etb_2xd_ldc" nd:nd-id="substeps_etb_2xd_ldc">
                    <substep class="- topic/li task/substep ">
                        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">点击菜单栏"Zotero"</cmd>
                    </substep>
                    <substep class="- topic/li task/substep ">
                        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">点击"设置"</cmd>
                    </substep>
                    <substep class="- topic/li task/substep ">
                        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">点击"常规"</cmd>
                    </substep>
                    <substep class="- topic/li task/substep ">
                        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">在"基于关键词和主题词自动为条目添加标签"前面方框内点击，使他处于不选中状态。
                                <image class="- topic/image " href="file:/Users/mac/Desktop/2024入学/课程/技术写作/中期报告/6.%20标签管理/6-image/3%20导入文献不自动导入关键词作为标签.png" id="unique_3_Connect_42_image_rt4_kzd_ldc" nd:nd-id="image_rt4_kzd_ldc" placement="inline" width="300"/></cmd>
                    </substep>
                </substeps>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">为文献添加新标签</cmd>
                <substeps class="- topic/ol task/substeps " id="unique_3_Connect_42_substeps_ngk_vwd_ldc" nd:nd-id="substeps_ngk_vwd_ldc">
                    <substep class="- topic/li task/substep ">
                        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">选中文献并打开标签面板</cmd>
                    </substep>
                    <substep class="- topic/li task/substep ">
                        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">点击"+" 图标，输入标签名称，按回车键完成。      <image class="- topic/image " href="file:/Users/mac/Desktop/2024入学/课程/技术写作/中期报告/6.%20标签管理/6-image/4%20给一篇文献添加标签.png" id="unique_3_Connect_42_image_lbd_1xd_ldc" nd:nd-id="image_lbd_1xd_ldc" placement="inline" width="300"/></cmd>
                    </substep>
                </substeps>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">为多篇文献添加现有标签</cmd>
                <substeps class="- topic/ol task/substeps " id="unique_3_Connect_42_substeps_x1k_jyd_ldc" nd:nd-id="substeps_x1k_jyd_ldc">
                    <substep class="- topic/li task/substep ">
                        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">将选中文献拖动到左下角的标签区域</cmd>
                    </substep>
                </substeps>
            </step>
        </steps>
    </taskbody>
</task><task class="- topic/topic task/task " id="unique_4" topicrefclass="- map/topicref " nd:nd-id="tag_search_and_color" oid="tag_search_and_color" specializations="@props/deliveryTarget">
    <title class="- topic/title "><ph class="- topic/ph topic/title-wrapper ">6.3 搜索和设置标签颜色</ph></title>
    <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc ">通过颜色区分标签，并快速搜索需要的标签。</shortdesc>
    <taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody ">
        <context class="- topic/section task/context ">
            <p class="- topic/p "/>
        </context>
        <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">为标签指定颜色</cmd>
                <substeps class="- topic/ol task/substeps " id="unique_4_Connect_42_substeps_cy4_vzd_ldc" nd:nd-id="substeps_cy4_vzd_ldc">
                    <substep class="- topic/li task/substep ">
                        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">右击标签并选择"分配颜色"。    <image class="- topic/image " href="file:/Users/mac/Desktop/2024入学/课程/技术写作/中期报告/6.%20标签管理/6-image/6%20给标签指定颜色%201.png" id="unique_4_Connect_42_image_x42_3d2_ldc" nd:nd-id="image_x42_3d2_ldc" placement="inline" width="300"/></cmd>
                    </substep>
                    <substep class="- topic/li task/substep ">
                        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">选择颜色并设置位置。                <image class="- topic/image " href="file:/Users/mac/Desktop/2024入学/课程/技术写作/中期报告/6.%20标签管理/6-image/6%20给标签指定颜色%202.png" id="unique_4_Connect_42_image_tvs_wzd_ldc" nd:nd-id="image_tvs_wzd_ldc" placement="inline" width="300"/></cmd>
                    </substep>
                </substeps>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">搜索标签</cmd>
                <substeps class="- topic/ol task/substeps " id="unique_4_Connect_42_substeps_wq2_yzd_ldc" nd:nd-id="substeps_wq2_yzd_ldc">
                    <substep class="- topic/li task/substep ">
                        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">在标签区域底部输入标签名称。  <image class="- topic/image " href="file:/Users/mac/Desktop/2024入学/课程/技术写作/中期报告/6.%20标签管理/6-image/7%20搜索标签.png" id="unique_4_Connect_42_image_cdc_112_ldc" nd:nd-id="image_cdc_112_ldc" placement="inline" width="300"/></cmd>
                    </substep>
                </substeps>
            </step>
        </steps>
    </taskbody>
</task><task class="- topic/topic task/task " id="unique_5" topicrefclass="- map/topicref " nd:nd-id="bulk_delere_tags" oid="bulk_delere_tags" specializations="@props/deliveryTarget">
    <title class="- topic/title "><ph class="- topic/ph topic/title-wrapper ">6.4 批量删除标签</ph></title>
    <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc ">同时从多篇文献中删除某一标签。</shortdesc>
    <taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody ">
        <context class="- topic/section task/context ">
            <p class="- topic/p "/>
        </context>
        <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">选中需要处理的文献。</cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">按住"shift"或"Ctrl"键选择多篇文献。</cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">拖动选中的文献到需要删除的标签上。</cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">标签将从这些文献中移除。</cmd>
            </step>
        </steps>
    </taskbody>
</task></topic></map>